{"_path":"/blog/en/autumn-in-ardennes","_dir":"en","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"Autumn in Belgian Ardennes","description":"Our plan was as follows: on Saturday we decided to do a full-day hiking and on Sunday nothing but chill. Bouillon is located by the river Semois. Although hills around are not very high, hikers can still choose a lot of uphill trails.","published_at":"2018-10-22","intro":"Last weekend we decided with Jola to go for a spontaneous trip to Ardennes in Belgium. We hoped to see beautiful autumn. Right after work we rented a car and hit the road and after only few hours we arrived to Bouillon.","category":"photography","background":"v1620582911/stories/autumn-in-ardennes/457_enaiv7.jpg","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Our plan was as follows: on Saturday we decided to do a full-day hiking and on Sunday nothing but chill. Bouillon is located by the river Semois. Although hills around are not very high, hikers can still choose a lot of uphill trails."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"66.666","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620582912/stories/autumn-in-ardennes/455_qhei72.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"66.666","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620582911/stories/autumn-in-ardennes/456_jtytr3.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"64","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620582911/stories/autumn-in-ardennes/457_enaiv7.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"66.666","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620582912/stories/autumn-in-ardennes/458_mwd2vf.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"66.666","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620582912/stories/autumn-in-ardennes/459_p8fjjn.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"66.666","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620582912/stories/autumn-in-ardennes/460_tew9w5.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"66.666","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620582912/stories/autumn-in-ardennes/461_ozc5a6.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"One of the most popular spots is a viewpoint with a view at The Giant's Tomb (fr. Le Tombeau du GÃ©ant). It is a small hill in the bend of the river, covered by trees that form a shape of a cross (as Internet claims, I think it's hardly visible)."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"66.666","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620582912/stories/autumn-in-ardennes/462_wmheym.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"56.25","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620582912/stories/autumn-in-ardennes/463_cgkb4p.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"50","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620582912/stories/autumn-in-ardennes/464_r2xkyy.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Plan for Sunday was definitely more relaxed. I decided to shoot sunrise by the Tomb of the Giant, but when I arrived there everything was covered in the mist and there was absolutely no view. I did some driving trying to find nice compositions to picture this sunny, calm morning."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"66.666","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620582913/stories/autumn-in-ardennes/469_xnyvxk.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"66.666","src":"https://res.cloudinary